&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mergers &amp;amp; Acquisitions Attorney (1-8 Years)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our strategically growing law firm is seeking a talented Mergers &amp;amp; Acquisitions Associate Attorney to join our corporate practice. This role offers the opportunity to work on sophisticated transactions for clients nationwide, alongside a collaborative team of experienced attorneys. The ideal candidate will thrive in a dynamic environment that combines the resources of a large firm with the flexibility to deliver customized, business-focused solutions to clients facing complex transactions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
