&lt;li&gt;Assist in and manage all phases of M&amp;amp;A and investment transactions, including structuring, due diligence, negotiation, drafting, execution, closing, and post-closing integration;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft and negotiate definitive transaction documents, including purchase agreements, disclosure schedules, and ancillary agreements;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct and manage legal due diligence reviews and summarize findings for deal teams and clients;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze legal, regulatory, and competitive considerations affecting transactions across a variety of industries;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise clients on corporate governance and general corporate matters;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interact directly with business executives, investors, and other transaction stakeholders;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively as part of a high-performing deal team, with increasing responsibility as experience grows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Ideal Candidate Will Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
